# Turso Setup

1. Install the Turso CLI: `curl -sSfL https://get.tur.so/install.sh | bash`
2. Login: `turso auth login`
3. Create a database: `turso db create my-db`
4. Get the database URL: `turso db show my-db --url`
5. Get the auth token: `turso db tokens create my-db`
6. Update your `.env` file with `DATABASE_URL` and `DATABASE_AUTH_TOKEN`.
